All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary Exception Summary 
    Class Description
    AnimalController
    Manager that facilitates the movement of animals on the map.
    BadSaveException
    Exception thrown when a save file is invalid or contains incorrect data.
    Collectable
    Denotes an entity that can be collected by the User in the simulation.
    CollectEvent
    The collection of an entity that implemented Collectable by a User.
    Coordinate
    A coordinate is a representation of the X and Y positions on a graphical map.
    This X, Y position can be used to calculate the index of a Tile in the scenario tile map depending on the currently active scenario.
    CoordinateOutOfBoundsException
    Exception thrown when the program attempts to access a Tile using an invalid Coordinate / index.
    Encodable
    Denotes a class whose state can be encoded and represented as a String.
    Entity
    An entity is an item that can exist as an inhabitant of a tile.
    Event
    An event that occurs in the Scenario.
    Fauna
    Fauna is all the animal life present in a particular region or time.
    Flora
    Flora is all the plant life present in a particular region or time, generally the naturally occurring (indigenous) native plants.
    Launcher
    Entry point for the GUI of the Research Simulation.
    Logger
    A detailed log that contains a record of Events and contains some event statistics.
    Movable
    Denotes a specific type of entity that can move around in the simulation.
    MoveEvent
    The movement of an entity from one coordinate to another (new) coordinate.
    NoSuchEntityException
    Exception thrown when attempting to get the entity at an empty tile.
    Scenario
    The scenario is the overriding class of the simulation.
    ScenarioCanvas
    Subclass of the JavaFX Canvas to represent the main elements of the Scenario graphically.
    ScenarioManager
    Singleton class which manages all the scenarios items.
    Size
    This enum governs the base attributes of each entity.
    Tile
    A tile on the scenario map that entities' items operate on.
    TileType
    Represents the type of terrain that is at a tile.
    User
    User is the player controlled character in the simulation.
    View
    View for the Research Simulation GUI.
    ViewModel
    View model for the Research Simulation GUI.
